flowchart TD
  subgraph ComposeStack
    OLLAMA[Ollama service\n(ollama/Dockerfile)]
    MEM0[Mem0-Supergateway (per-agent)\n(mem0chat/Dockerfile)\nports 8766-8772]
    CODE[Code Sandbox / Agent Gateway\n(hummusapiens/Dockerfile)]
  end

  subgraph External
    OCZ[OpenCode Zen API\nhttps://opencode.ai/zen/v1/chat/completions]
  end

  subgraph Standalone
    CLI[mem0chat CLI client\n(root Dockerfile)]
  end

  CLI -->|HTTP MCP requests| MEM0
  CLI -->|Inference requests| OCZ

  MEM0 -->|Embedding requests| OLLAMA

  CODE -->|Memory / MCP access| MEM0
  CODE -->|Embedding requests| OLLAMA
  CODE -->|Workspace mount| WORKSPACE[workspace/ volume]

  OLLAMA -->|Model storage| OLLAMAVOL[ollama_models volume]
  MEM0 -->|Memory store| MEM0VOL[mem0_data volume]
